title: Пять минут до метро
overview: Пять минут до метро is a Ukrainian serial released back in 2006. The plot reveals to viewers the lives of four married couples who live in the neighborhood and communicate with each other on a daily basis on a variety of topics while discussing various ongoing issues. As expected, serious quarrels and conflicts arise between them, feelings flare up and fade away, and many things happen that are characteristic of such a relationship.
